timing_derate_...eference_point(25.10)  timing_derate_...eference_point(25.10)

Name
       timing_derate_aocv_reference_point

Syntax
       timing_derate_aocv_reference_point {1 | 0}

       Default: 1

       Allows  specification  of  reference point for AOCV factors. As per the
       current AOCV library definitions, the AOCV reference  point  is  always
       expected to be set at 1.0.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

